         <p class="- topic/p ">One power block consists of:<ul class="- topic/ul ">
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">25 kVA: Two power modules, or </p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">12.5 kVA: One power module with a capacitor board and an empty
power module box<fn class="- topic/fn ">The 12.5 kVA power block can be added to a 25
kVA power block to make a 37.5 kVA UPS)</fn>
                  </p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Controller box</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Power connection board</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Fan with fan monitor</p>
               </li>
            </ul>
         </p>
